{% doc %}
  @prompt
    I want to design a “brand origin / why we exist” section for a premium hair supplement brand (Revistem).
    
    Context:
    - Brand tone: clinical, honest, evidence-based, non-marketing
    - Not emotional storytelling, but rational and credible
    - Audience: informed users, often already researching hair loss treatments
    - Aesthetic: minimal, clean, similar to Aesop / The Ordinary
    - No hype, no exaggerated claims
    
    Core idea:
    The brand was created because existing supplements were either superficial or generic, with low doses and marketing-driven formulations.
    
    Goal:
    Create a strong, credible “origin story” section that builds trust and explains why Revistem exists.
    
    Content to adapt (Spanish, you can refine but keep meaning):
    
    "Revistem nació de una búsqueda personal. Buscaba un suplemento capilar que no se limitara a poner biotina y saw palmetto en una cápsula y llamarlo 'fórmula avanzada'. Quería algo que atacara el problema desde dentro: soporte folicular real, pero también soporte celular, mitocondrial y antioxidante sistémico.
    
    Lo que encontré en el mercado era o demasiado superficial o demasiado genérico. Fórmulas con ingredientes interesantes en dosis que no sirven para nada. Marketing construido sobre claims que ninguna etiqueta podía sostener.
    
    Así que decidí formularlo desde cero, con un criterio claro: cada ingrediente tiene que estar por una razón, a una dosis que tenga sentido, y tiene que poder explicarse sin exagerar.
    
    Revistem es el resultado de ese proceso."
    
    Requirements:
    - Break the text into short, readable paragraphs (max 2–3 lines each)
    - Improve flow and clarity without changing meaning
    - Maintain a serious, credible tone
    - Avoid sounding like a marketing story
    - Highlight key ideas subtly through spacing and structure
    
    Design direction:
    - Section background color: #F9F2E9
    - Left-aligned text block (not centered)
    - Generous white space
    - No cards, no boxes
    - Editorial feel (like a long-form article)
    - Comfortable max-width for readability (not full width)
    
    Also:
    - Suggest a refined section title (Spanish)
    - Suggest paragraph structure (how many blocks and order)
    - Suggest subtle typography hierarchy (title vs body)
    
    Output:
    - Final Spanish copy (clean and structured)
    - Section title options
    - Layout/UX suggestion
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-brand-origin-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.padding_top }}px 0 {{ block.settings.padding_bottom }}px;
  }

  .ai-brand-origin-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.content_max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 {{ block.settings.horizontal_padding }}px;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-brand-origin-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding-left: {{ block.settings.desktop_offset }}px;
    }
  }

  .ai-brand-origin-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.title_size_mobile }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.title_weight }};
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.title_spacing }}px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-brand-origin-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.title_size }}px;
    }
  }

  .ai-brand-origin-paragraph-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.body_size_mobile }}px;
    line-height: {{ block.settings.body_line_height }};
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.paragraph_spacing }}px;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .ai-brand-origin-paragraph-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.body_size }}px;
    }
  }

  .ai-brand-origin-paragraph-{{ ai_gen_id }}:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div class="ai-brand-origin-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-brand-origin-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    {% if block.settings.title != blank %}
      <h2 class="ai-brand-origin-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.title }}</h2>
    {% endif %}

    {% if block.settings.paragraph_1 != blank %}
      <div class="ai-brand-origin-paragraph-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.paragraph_1 }}</div>
    {% endif %}

    {% if block.settings.paragraph_2 != blank %}
      <div class="ai-brand-origin-paragraph-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.paragraph_2 }}</div>
    {% endif %}

    {% if block.settings.paragraph_3 != blank %}
      <div class="ai-brand-origin-paragraph-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.paragraph_3 }}</div>
    {% endif %}

    {% if block.settings.paragraph_4 != blank %}
      <div class="ai-brand-origin-paragraph-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.paragraph_4 }}</div>
    {% endif %}

    {% if block.settings.paragraph_5 != blank %}
      <div class="ai-brand-origin-paragraph-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.paragraph_5 }}</div>
    {% endif %}

    {% if block.settings.paragraph_6 != blank %}
      <div class="ai-brand-origin-paragraph-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.paragraph_6 }}</div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Brand origin",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Content"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "title",
      "label": "Title",
      "default": "Por qué existe Revistem"
    },
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "paragraph_1",
      "label": "Paragraph 1",
      "default": "Revistem nació de una búsqueda personal. Buscaba un suplemento capilar que no se limitara a poner biotina y saw palmetto en una cápsula y llamarlo 'fórmula avanzada'."
    },
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "paragraph_2",
      "label": "Paragraph 2",
      "default": "Quería algo que atacara el problema desde dentro: soporte folicular real, pero también soporte celular, mitocondrial y antioxidante sistémico."
    },
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "paragraph_3",
      "label": "Paragraph 3",
      "default": "Lo que encontré en el mercado era o demasiado superficial o demasiado genérico."
    },
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "paragraph_4",
      "label": "Paragraph 4",
      "default": "Fórmulas con ingredientes interesantes en dosis que no sirven para nada. Marketing construido sobre claims que ninguna etiqueta podía sostener."
    },
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "paragraph_5",
      "label": "Paragraph 5",
      "default": "Así que decidí formularlo desde cero, con un criterio claro: cada ingrediente tiene que estar por una razón, a una dosis que tenga sentido, y tiene que poder explicarse sin exagerar."
    },
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "paragraph_6",
      "label": "Paragraph 6",
      "default": "Revistem es el resultado de ese proceso."
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Layout"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "content_max_width",
      "label": "Content max width",
      "min": 400,
      "max": 900,
      "step": 20,
      "unit": "px",
      "default": 680
